{"tid":8654,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【邪門玩意】電話爆Mon記","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T10:58:34.000Z","uid":30288,"like":13,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe610526070616dfcc0c0ecb6b254013cc8928b3","tid":8654,"uid":30288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"各手機台巴打&hellip;我來啦！<br />\n<br />\n上星期六&hellip;係街邊打邊爐期間順眼望下靚女&hellip;望到入神期間&hellip;我老婆特然係後面話&hellip;條女係唔係好正呀？！嚇到我手軟&hellip;成部電話（大陸版華為Mate8）就咁墮地&hellip;初時仲以為無野，因為有皮既外殼&hellip;點知一拿起&hellip;除左個mon碎左，我個心都碎埋&hellip;唉&hellip;（只怪自己性能力高強）&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221924_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221924_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=ae26d118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁無辦法啦都要去整架&hellip;，據我所知&hellip;如果去深圳華為整的話&hellip;要成7&times;&times;-8&times;&times;人仔最少&hellip;所以上淘寶網Search下&hellip;俾我搵到&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221404_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221404_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=e20548c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221416_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221416_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=4862eb25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手就問個客服點搞？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221624_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221624_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=f520aaa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221636_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221636_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=5f47094e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221655_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221655_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=cc79a80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221707_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221707_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=c878e467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/221721_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F221721_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=4c9882ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個電話要返大陸寄的&hellip;<br />\n一出羅湖關上地面既左手面再上一層行到尾就有速遞&hellip;可以跟據個客服俾既地址寄出就ok&hellip;寄費10蚊8蚊人仔only<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/172216_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F172216_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=045eb6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞好&hellip;預備回收<br />\n<br />\n故事結局係點？&hellip;請繼續追Post！"},{"pid":"8cfacee1612902a9aba55b2b41b606aacb614aa1","tid":8654,"uid":30288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d509175b1ad63123b3375ffbcd91732ceb60c628","tid":8654,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"大閘蟹食你唔死<img src=\"/